---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import AffiliateButton from '../../components/AffiliateButton.astro';

const title = "AG1 versus FS Greens: Which Superfood Powder is Right for You in 2026";
const description = "We compare AG1 by Athletic Greens and FS Greens. Read our objective breakdown of formulations, benefits, and costs to find the best green powder for your wellness routine.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <article>
      <!-- Article Header -->
      <header class="mb-12 text-center">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-4 block font-semibold">Supplement Comparison</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          AG1 versus FS Greens: Which Superfood Powder is Right for You in 2026
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-8">
          <span class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Editorial Review</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Updated May 2026</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-12 shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
        <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1346347/pexels-photo-1346347.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="AG1 vs FS Greens" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>

      <!-- Article Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-stone prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-700">
        <p class="lead text-xl italic text-slate-900 mb-8" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          In the busy world of wellness, green powders have become an essential habit for people looking to bridge their nutritional gaps. However, with the market giant AG1 and the rising specialist FS Greens leading the pack, it can be hard to know which one truly deserves a spot in your morning routine.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-10">
          As part of our commitment at Wellness Sanctuary to provide clear and honest health analysis, we have broken down the formulations, benefits, and daily costs to help you make an informed decision.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">1. Formulation Breakdown</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Athletic Greens AG1</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
            This is a massive all in one formula containing 75 ingredients. It includes vitamins, minerals, probiotics, and adaptogens. The goal here is simple: replace multiple different supplements with just a single scoop.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">FS Greens by Free Soul</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
            This takes a more streamlined and targeted approach featuring 21 key ingredients. It focuses heavily on digestive health and hormonal balance, completely avoiding any artificial sweeteners.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">2. Comparison Table</h2>
        
        <p class="mb-6">
          We compared the core elements of both products to give you a clear picture of what you are paying for.
        </p>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-emerald-600">
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Feature</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">AG1</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">FS Greens</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Ingredient Count</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">75 Ingredients</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">21 Ingredients</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Primary Focus</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Performance and Energy</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Digestion and Wellness</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Probiotics</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">7.2 Billion CFU</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Targeted Strains</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/50">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Flavor Profile</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Mild Pineapple Vanilla</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Mango Mint or Natural</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Price per Serving</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Around €3.30</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Around €1.20</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">3. The Editorial Verdict</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-emerald-600 pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Choose AG1 if</p>
            <p class="text-sm">You want a comprehensive nutritional insurance policy that covers everything from immunity to stress management, assuming your budget allows for a premium investment.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <AffiliateButton id="ag1" text="Try Athletic Greens AG1" />
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-[#b7ccb9] pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Choose FS Greens if</p>
            <p class="text-sm">You prioritize gut health, prefer a cleaner and shorter ingredient list, or are looking for the best value for your money without sacrificing any quality.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <AffiliateButton id="fs-greens" text="Try Free Soul FS Greens" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-slate-200 my-12" />

        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-stone-200">
          <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">🩺</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Why Trust Our Analysis</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-8">
            At Wellness Sanctuary, we do not just list products. We analyze the clinical data and formulations to ensure you make the best choice for your long term health.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Still undecided</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-6">
            Take our quick Personalized Health Quiz to find the exact supplement match for your unique metabolism and goals.
          </p>
          <a href="/quiz" class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-all">
            Find My Program
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
